name: Crypto Faun 02 - April 2021
description: A one-of-a-kind stunning 4K resolution piece of animated digital art. A combination of hand drawn work combined with digitally reworked, analog glitch art. This particular piece is part of a series of 5 crypto fauns released in 2021. Every piece is signed by the artist. For more info on artist LotteZ visit: www.lottez.com
